 All this shows that the thorough implementation of the joint declaration precisely means the way for achieving reunification. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The authorities should immediately stop suppression on the strength of the "National Security Law", evil law against reunification, and release all pro-reunification patriotic figures including Yun, it stressed.

